data.description: Welcome to your dream Key West Style home! This charming 4-bed, 2-bath furnished residence is tailor-made for a buyer seeking both style and practicality. Inside, features elegant tiles throughout the main areas, promising both comfort and resilience. Your private backyard oasis beckons, complete with an above-ground pool cocooned by a privacy fence, offering the ultimate in tranquility. Welcome guests via the spacious front porch and host gatherings on the decorative paver patio. Rest easy knowing your home is fully hurricane-ready with a protective metal roof and full hurricane panels, ensuring peace of mind during storm seasons. Nestled in a top-rated school district and conveniently located near shopping, dining, and I-95 and the Turnpike. This home is an absolute MUST SEE for those craving a light-filled retreat with a seamless fusion of indoor-outdoor living.
